@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_osotzh(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.cos((0.22 / (v2 + 0.59 / v0 + 0.28)))
    tmp = 0.47
    v1 = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v2 + 0.27)) / ((v1 + 0.82 * v0 + 0.48) / (v1 + 0.73 - v2 + 0.09)))
    tmp = v2
    tmp = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
